channel.title: Error with compiler and saving plz help

Also i have this error when i compile my server:
antilag.java:4: error while writing antilag: antilag.class (Access is denied) public class antilag ^ Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. 1 error Press any key to continue . . .
And one more thing lol when eva i log out and on it doesent save properly and i have to start all over again how can i fix that? sry bout all the questions ...
